{"tid":2228197,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"管浩鳴：陳同佳的律師下周聯絡台灣 盼有改過自新的機會","createTime":"2020-10-03T11:11:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-03T11:40:27.000Z","uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0ded6f489b72ca7bd60c5b74d671f1bf3c8e7e8d","tid":2228197,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T11:11:00.000Z","msg":"陳同佳何時來台？管浩鳴指律師周一晤台灣部門<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/resizer/fGb3tfseNA5Bw6v5IxZhIYl1ikg=/720x405/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/XMIQDEZDKFDHHIU2RYW6V72DZI.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfGb3tfseNA5Bw6v5IxZhIYl1ikg%3D%2F720x405%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FXMIQDEZDKFDHHIU2RYW6V72DZI.jpg&h=2ab10d95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n管浩鳴牧師指陳同佳的代表律師下周會跟台灣相關部門商談。香港《蘋果動新聞》<br />\n<br />\n香港青年陳同佳2018年在台灣殺死女友潘曉穎，在香港未能因殺人罪名受審，還因為他的案件掀起香港「反送中」抗爭浪潮，陳同佳出獄近一年，潘曉穎母親近日連番喊話，要他來台灣投案接受法律制裁，<span class=\"red\">一直照顧陳同佳的香港聖公會教省秘書長管浩鳴牧師今對記者表示，他一直希望死者能得以安息，陳同佳有改過自新的機會，雙方家庭都能重新生活。</span><br />\n<br />\n管浩鳴牧師昨（2日）對公開陳同佳的23秒錄音，表示最快本月內會赴台自首（投案）。潘曉穎母親質疑錄音檔案的真實性，管牧指有關錄音於周三（9月30日）錄製，「我想他父親已經回答了」。<span class=\"red\">至於為何陳同佳不能立刻啟程，管牧師未正面回應</span>，僅指陳同佳的台灣代表律師會於星期一（5日）與台灣相關部門會面商討，有進一步消息再會對外公佈，「等台灣律師去搞，法律問題我真的沒辦法回答大家」。<br />\n<br />\n陳同佳昨日透過管牧師發放23秒錄音，向潘曉穎父母道歉：「潘爸爸、潘媽媽你們好，我是陳同佳。我再次就曉穎的事情向你們道歉，我去台灣的想法一直都沒改變過，我會請我的律師安排返台灣自首的事情，請你們放心。」陳同佳父親昨日回應香港《蘋果》查詢時表示，支持兒子去台灣自首，並指不排除陪他赴台自首。（國際中心╱綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201003/EOWF3T2NGVCDZH3YDEIKP5EX5Y/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201003%2FEOWF3T2NGVCDZH3YDEIKP5EX5Y%2F&d=YLq6vaBnyeHQX05GIPWJdlxDM7DnHmdvX2f5RcY9ddA%3D&h=d21c8542\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201003%2FEOWF3T2NGVCDZH3YDEIKP5EX5Y%2F&h=38f42c9b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/20201003/EOWF3T2NGVCDZH3YDEIKP5EX5Y/</a>"},{"pid":"ef2e935ab7d54d3d225880168f8c934fe397af94","tid":2228197,"uid":2054,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T11:16:09.000Z","msg":"幾時聯絡大劉呀屌你老母死"},{"pid":"2cbb0638a583fef0db0e87ccfb2f939284ef595b","tid":2228197,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T11:31:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d8f542073c0042b219565ec1f304bbc851f4bf03","tid":2228197,"uid":223741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T11:37:00.000Z","msg":"今日飛唔得嘅"},{"pid":"03fea5f84cbeb06943a59897bcea27a00ba5dea4","tid":2228197,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2cbb0638a583fef0db0e87ccfb2f939284ef595b","tid":2228197,"uid":284432,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T11:31:34.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T11:37:34.000Z","msg":"台灣講咗唔一定會死刑 冇話一定唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"128a0b8eb5a06adcd2507126e5d50e8f13bb6d3f","tid":2228197,"uid":70336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-03T11:40:27.000Z","msg":"拖。。。拖。。。拖。。。。"}]}